  "variables": [
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "rose",
      "description": "教程主题（要画的对象）。例如：rose / peony 牡丹 / cherry blossom 樱花 / lotus 荷花 / koi fish 锦鲤 / hummingbird 蜂鸟 / mushroom 蘑菇 / autumn leaf / pinecone / lemon。建议用单一明确的物体。",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "subject"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "a single blooming pink rose with soft curling petals and a few green leaves",
      "description": "主题的具体形态描述（颜色、姿态、细节）。例如：「半开的白牡丹，三片飘逸花瓣」「侧面游动的橙白锦鲤，鱼鳍展开」。这是控制最终图像具象效果的关键。",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "subject_descriptor"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Step 1: Base Wash",
      "description": "步骤 1 的标题（左上格）。默认是「底色平涂 / 浅色打底」对应英文。",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "step1_label"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Sketch the rose outline lightly in pencil. Apply a wet-on-wet pale pink wash over the petals, leaving the lightest highlights as bare paper.",
      "description": "步骤 1 的操作说明（什么颜色、什么手法、画到什么程度）。会以小字标签形式画在格子里。",
      "kind": "multiline",
      "name": "step1_action"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Step 2: Build Form",
      "description": "步骤 2 的标题（右上格）。默认「塑造形体 / 增加纹理」。",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "step2_label"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Add a second layer of medium pink to define petal curls. Drop in soft sap green for the leaves and stem while the wash is still damp for natural blending.",
      "description": "步骤 2 的操作说明。",
      "kind": "multiline",
      "name": "step2_action"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Step 3: Deepen Layers",
      "description": "步骤 3 的标题（左下格）。默认「添加层次 / 深化细节」。",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "step3_label"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Layer deeper crimson into the petal shadows and the throat of the rose. Add cooler shadow tones to the underside of the leaves.",
      "description": "步骤 3 的操作说明。",
      "kind": "multiline",
      "name": "step3_action"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Step 4: Final Details",
      "description": "步骤 4 的标题（右下格）。默认「最后润饰 / 完整画面」。",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "step4_label"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Once dry, use a fine brush to add petal veins, leaf veins, and the darkest accent shadows. Lift small highlights with a damp clean brush to finish.",
      "description": "步骤 4 的操作说明。",
      "kind": "multiline",
      "name": "step4_action"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Opera Pink, Permanent Rose, Alizarin Crimson, Sap Green, Olive Green, Burnt Sienna",
      "description": "本次教程使用的颜料名称列表（会作为色卡标注画在步骤旁边）。建议写真实的水彩颜料品名（W&N、Schmincke、好赛贝等）。每色之间用逗号分隔。",
      "kind": "multiline",
      "name": "color_palette"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "form structure & light/shadow relationship of the rose, with arrows showing light direction and labels for petal layers, core shadow, cast shadow",
      "description": "中央草图示意图的内容焦点。默认展示形体结构 + 光影关系；也可改成「比例分割」「构图安排」「色彩冷暖分布」等其他教学重点。",
